<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HOME</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include('components/header') %>

    <main class="main">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="page-title"><%= pageTitle %></h2>

            <!-- EJS 스터디 리스트 -->
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>반복문</p>
                    <p>&lt;% todos.forEach() %&gt;</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>조건문</p>
                    <p>&lt;% if() %&gt; &lt;% else %&gt;</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>include 문법</p>
                    <p>&lt;%- include('파일경로') %&gt;</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>변수 출력</p>
                    <p>&lt;%= %&gt;</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>HTML escape 없이 출력</p>
                    <p>&lt;%- %&gt;</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>partials 나누기 (components) : header + item(옵션)</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>EJS 내부에서 JavaScript 활용하기</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
            
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>